{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"443a0e1572","title":"关于容许新闻记者进入开城地区问题致李克农电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"260b264740","index":0,"year":1951,"month":7,"day":12,"articleId":"443a0e1572"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"b7b5aba6aa","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"443a0e1572","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李克农，当时任中央人民政府外交部副部长。"},{"id":"d30f6f0477","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"443a0e1572","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"金，指朝鲜民主主义人民共和国首相金日成。彭，指中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员彭德怀。"}],"contents":[{"id":"edfb978603","type":"title","text":"关于容许新闻记者进人开城地区问题致李克农电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"443a0e1572"},{"id":"b7b5aba6aa","type":"paragraph","text":"克农，并告金、彭：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"443a0e1572"},{"id":"d30f6f0477","type":"paragraph","text":"在谈判恢复后讨论记者问题时，我方可同意在议程问题取得完全协议后，容许双方同等数目之记者到达开城地区，但不得进入会场。记者数目须估计我方能到者。我方记者主要在前方组织，北京方面亦可组织苏波捷等国的一些记者去。估计议程还会有许多大争辩，才能取得协议，那时我方可以组织一些记者去。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"443a0e1572"},{"id":"1c4bb94939","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"443a0e1572"},{"id":"e82286048f","type":"paragraph","text":"七月十二日廿四时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"443a0e1572"}],"page":{"id":"95abe48714","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"443a0e1572","start":444,"end":444}}}},"__N_SSG":true}